{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Selector (セレクター (CSS) )","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Glossary/CSS_Selector","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>CSS セレクター</strong>は CSS の規則の一部で、文書中のどの要素がルールと一致するかを記述します。一致した要素には規則で指定されたスタイルが適用されます。</p>\n<p>この CSS を見てください。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> green<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">div.warning</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2px solid yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> white<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> darkred<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0.8em 0.8em 0.6em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">#customized</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 16px Lucida Grande<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Arial<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Helvetica<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sans-serif<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>ここでのセレクターは <code>\"p\"</code> （すべての <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/p\"><code>&lt;p&gt;</code></a> 要素内の文字列に緑色を適用）、 <code>\"div.warning\"</code> （<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\">class</a> が <code>\"warning\"</code> であるすべての <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a> 要素が警告ボックスのように見えるようにする）、 <code>\"#customized\"</code> （<code>\"customized\"</code> の ID を持つ要素の基本フォントを 16 ピクセルの高さの Lucida Grande またはいくつかのフォールバックフォントに設定）です。</p>\n<p>この CSS を次のような HTML に適用します。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This is happy text.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>warning<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  Be careful! There are wizards present, and they are quick to anger!\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>customized<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This is happy text.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>warning<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    Be careful! There are wizards present, and they are quick to anger!\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>結果的に、ページの内容は次のように整形されます。</p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"glossary-selector-details sample\" id=\"frame_glossary-selector-details\" width=\"640\" height=\"210\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ja/docs/Glossary/CSS_Selector/_sample_.glossary-selector-details.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>\n<ol>\n  <li>CSS 入門内の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/Building_blocks/Selectors\">CSS セレクターについての詳細</a></li>\n  <li>基本的なセレクター\n    <ol>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Type_selectors\">要素型セレクター</a> <code>elementname</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Class_selectors\">クラスセレクター</a> <code>.classname</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/ID_selectors\">ID セレクター</a> <code>#idname</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Universal_selectors\">全称セレクター</a> <code>* ns|* *|*</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Attribute_selectors\">属性セレクター</a> <code>[attr=value]</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-classes\">状態セレクター</a> <code>a:active, a:visited</code></li>\n    </ol>\n  </li>\n  <li>グループ化セレクター\n    <ol>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Selector_list\">セレクターリスト</a> <code>A, B</code></li>\n    </ol>\n  </li>\n  <li>結合子\n    <ol>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Adjacent_sibling_combinator\">隣接兄弟セレクター</a> <code>A + B</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/General_sibling_combinator\">一般兄弟セレクター</a> <code>A ~ B</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Child_combinator\">子セレクター</a> <code>A &gt; B</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Descendant_combinator\">子孫セレクター</a> <code>A B</code></li>\n    </ol>\n  </li>\n  <li>擬似クラス・要素\n    <ol>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-classes\">擬似クラス</a> <code>:</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-elements\">擬似要素</a> <code>::</code></li>\n    </ol>\n  </li>\n  <li>技術リファレンス\n    <ol>\n      <li><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/selectors-3/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"Selectors Level&nbsp;3の仕様書\" rel=\" noopener\">Selectors Level&nbsp;3</a></li>\n    </ol>\n  </li>\n</ol>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"CSS セレクターは CSS の規則の一部で、文書中のどの要素がルールと一致するかを記述します。一致した要素には規則で指定されたスタイルが適用されます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Selector (CSS)","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Sélecteur CSS","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Selector (CSS)","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"CSS-селектор","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"CSS 选择器","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"CSS 選擇器","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/glossary/css_selector","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/glossary/css_selector/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary","title":"MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary/CSS_Selector","title":"Selector (セレクター (CSS) )"}],"pageTitle":"Selector (セレクター (CSS) ) - MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}